Class StaffmanagementImplTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.assertj.core.api.Assertions

        • io.oasp.module.test.common.base.ModuleTest
          • io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.staffmanagement.logic.impl.StaffmanagementImplTest

  • public class StaffmanagementImplTest
extends ModuleTest
    This class provides a basic implementation of a ModuleTest which employs the Mockito framework to provide fake objects to the SUT. For a limited number of test cases per class it can be convenient to use the annotation @InjectMocks to inject all needed mocks in the class under test.

      • testSaveStaffMember

        public void testSaveStaffMember()
        This test method updates a saved staffMemberEntity. It demonstrates the approach when there is a method call in the method under test. To solve this in the given case you need to override the @Inject of the tested method by using the appropriate setter setStaffMemberDao().
